                <mxCell id="102" value="&lt;span data-lucid-type=&quot;application/vnd.lucid.text&quot; data-lucid-content=&quot;{&amp;quot;t&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Multi-Tenancy Note: A User can belong to multiple companies simultaneously. Within each company they hold a specific role. A User who is Admin in Company A may only be a Member in Company B - roles are scoped per workspace.&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;m&amp;quot;:[{&amp;quot;s&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;n&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;c&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;v&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;#000000ff&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;e&amp;quot;:223}]}&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Multi-Tenancy Note: A User can belong to multiple companies simultaneously. Within each company they hold a specific role. A User who is Admin in Company A may only be a Member in Company B - roles are scoped per workspace.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="2346" y="6449" width="417" height="159" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="103" value="&lt;span data-lucid-type=&quot;application/vnd.lucid.text&quot; data-lucid-content=&quot;{&amp;quot;t&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;Flexible Roles: Admins can create roles with any name (e.g. Sales Lead, Project Owner). Each role has granular permissions assigned per module: CRM, Tasks, and Chat - with read, write, or admin levels.&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;m&amp;quot;:[{&amp;quot;s&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;n&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;c&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;v&amp;quot;:&amp;quot;#000000ff&amp;quot;,&amp;quot;e&amp;quot;:201}]}&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Flexible Roles: Admins can create roles with any name (e.g. Sales Lead, Project Owner). Each role has granular permissions assigned per module: CRM, Tasks, and Chat - with read, write, or admin levels.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="2346" y="6640" width="417" height="159" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
